reviews.content: Attended a wedding at this venue. They do not have wifi and the food was below average. The building is a bit old. I like nothing about this place.

Nhà hàng tiệc cưới Honey Moon, located on the second floor of the H3 Building at 384 Hoàng Diệu, Phường 6, Quận 4, Hồ Chí Minh City, is a prominent venue for wedding celebrations and events. The establishment boasts a modern and elegant …

Good place to go for a casual lunch in a formal atmosphere that even plays electronic dance techno.  Serves different flavours and types of meat but the meat portion is petite, however it is supplemented via the rice, veggies, soup, and watermelon slice(and tea drink) . Great job with changing the selection of meat often.
Good place for wedding party, the entrance made confused at the first time.
Nice food and staffs! 5 star if the pianist can play more songs!
Good foods, although not big enough but staffs always active and friendly
I have lunch here every working days.
